                "articleOutId": "c7c4731108694059aa5f0d023fe456d3",
                "html": "<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">最近开始在实际的国产化机器上折腾联邦学习环境，需要在一台断网的arm机器上装环境，记录一下踩过的坑。</p> \n<h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">现状和问题</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">有一台<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">不联网</strong>的<strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">arm架构</strong>的华为昇腾8卡机器可以用，驱动是装好的，但是本机环境只有python2.7。另外乙方公司打了一个docker，其中有torch适配昇腾卡的环境，但是没有装好transformers也没有装mindspore。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">因为torch适配昇腾算是“半个”国产化，我们还希望尝试一下100%的国产化，也就是把torch也替换成mindspore，transformers替换成mindformers。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">还考虑到我们和乙方公司要共用这一台机器，在本机装环境怕对对方造成影响。综合下来我们的目标是：构建一个arm架构机器上，可以基于在昇腾NPU上运行的mindspore运行联邦学习的docker镜像。</p> \n<h1 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">踩坑记录</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h1> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">arm架构的云服务器</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">最开始我觉得要build arm架构的镜像，就必须找arm架构的机器（后面有跨平台解决方案）。所以首先是需要找一台（最好是免费的）arm架构的机器，华为云平台最便宜的也要20一小时，还好启智平台https://openi.org.cn/有免费的可以用，每天只要开机就送积分。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/9499/44f706e0-82c8-47d5-9037-dbbd6b7fe59e.png\" alt=\"image\" style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n   image \n </figcaption> \n</figure> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">这个机器装docker会报错，而且考虑了一下即使装了docker，自己写DockerFile从0开始build也是很大的工程。决定先尝试一下只下载依赖包，在已经存在的镜像上修改。</p> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">在mac上build arm镜像</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">后来又查到其实docker已经支持了 https://docs.docker.com/build/building/multi-platform/#why-multi-platform-builds，只需要配置一下支持多平台的builder，然后就可以用--platform参数生成不同平台的镜像了。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/9499/8e80d0e3-52fb-41de-8cfc-6279c1418eb3.png\" alt=\"image\" style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n   image \n </figcaption> \n</figure> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">貌似builder本身也是一个镜像，有running或者pause状态。注意这个builder是Multi-platform ready，而默认的builder是single platform。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/9499/85e491ad-e467-445d-be3d-c5396bd35208.png\" alt=\"image\" style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"> \n <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: center; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n   image \n </figcaption> \n</figure> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">离线安装python包</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">坑1: pypi下载的whl不包含依赖</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">运行pip install xxxx.whl还会找他的依赖，如果离线的机器上没有，还是装不上。解决方案是用pip download，可以把全部依赖都下载下来。</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">坑2: python版本适配</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">类似cp39-cp39这样的强制python3.9版本，前后都不兼容。py3-none这样的不限制python版本随便装。</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">坑3: pip download只能单个下载</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">pip download -r requirements.txt批量下载依赖失败，本地并没有得到whl包。只好写个for循环一个一个下载。</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">坑4: 云平台不支持大文件下载</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">假设下载好的依赖包都放在req文件夹下，平台不支持100M以上的文件下载。</p> \n<pre class=\"custom\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; background: url(https://files.mdnice.com/user/3441/876cad08-0422-409d-bb5a-08afec5da8ee.svg); height: 30px; width: 100%; background-size: 40px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: #282c34; margin-bottom: -7px; border-radius: 5px; background-position: 10px 10px;\"></span><code class=\"hljs\" style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; color: #abb2bf; padding-top: 15px; background: #282c34; border-radius: 5px; display: -webkit-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px;\">tar&nbsp;-czvf&nbsp;req.tar.gz&nbsp;req<br>split&nbsp;-b&nbsp;95M&nbsp;req10.tar.gz&nbsp;req.tar.gz.part-<br></code></pre> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">这样会把所有包压缩&amp;拆分成不超过95M的n个小文件。下载下来之后再合并&amp;解压</p> \n<pre class=\"custom\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; background: url(https://files.mdnice.com/user/3441/876cad08-0422-409d-bb5a-08afec5da8ee.svg); height: 30px; width: 100%; background-size: 40px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: #282c34; margin-bottom: -7px; border-radius: 5px; background-position: 10px 10px;\"></span><code class=\"hljs\" style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; color: #abb2bf; padding-top: 15px; background: #282c34; border-radius: 5px; display: -webkit-box; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px;\">cat&nbsp;req.tar.gz.part-*&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;req.tar.gz<br>tar&nbsp;-zxvf&nbsp;req.tar.gz<br></code></pre> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">即可得到原来的文件夹</p> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">坑5: 离线装python包的相互依赖</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">把req文件夹传到断网服务器上之后会有个问题：假设一个python包引用了很多包，被引用的包之间还是相互依赖的，就必须按照先后顺序来装。这个就非常麻烦了，要不手动试（依赖不多还好），要不从metadata里把结构梳理出来。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">后来查到一个终极解决方案</p> \n<pre class=\"custom\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px; text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; background: url(https://files.mdnice.com/user/3441/876cad08-0422-409d-bb5a-08afec5da8ee.svg); height: 30px; width: 100%; background-size: 40px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: #282c34; margin-bottom: -7px; borde